POPE FACT
---------
http://popefact.com
Carlos d'Avis

Here, in its simple glory, is the PHP codebase for the first and only version of the POPE FACT website. Feel free to modify or reuse the code however you like. I offer no support or warranty. 

INSTALLATION
------------
1. Copy the files to your web server. You might want to update the .htaccess file. 
2. Do you have a MySQL database? Please create one. 
3. Import the schema from popefact.sql into your new database. 
4. Copy inc/config-example.inc to inc/config.inc. 
5. Update config.inc with your database connection details. 
6. Go! 

